{"id":750134,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Donald_May","text":"Donald May (born February 22, 1927) is an American actor. He is best known for his role as Adam Drake in the soap opera \"The Edge of Night\" from 1967 to 1977. His movie appearances include \"The Crowded Sky\" (1960), \"Kisses for My President\" (1964) and \"Follow Me, Boys!\" (1966).\nMay's other TV acting credits include \"The West Point Story\", \"Colt.45\", \"Sugarfoot\", \"Cheyenne\", \"77 Sunset Strip\", \"Hawaiian Eye\", \"Surfside 6\", \"The Roaring 20's\", \"Men into Space\", \"Barnaby Jones\", \"The Dukes of Hazzard\", \"Dallas\", \"Texas\", \"Falcon Crest\", \"Fantasy Island\", \"One Life to Live\", \"All My Children\" and \"L.A. Law\".\nMay was born in Chicago, Illinois. He had two children with his first wife. He later married actress Carla Borelli.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Americans","surface_form":"American","offset":42},{"uri":"Soap_opera","surface_form":"soap opera","offset":109},{"uri":"The_Edge_of_Night","surface_form":"The Edge of Night","offset":121},{"uri":"The_Crowded_Sky","surface_form":"The Crowded Sky","offset":190},{"uri":"Kisses_for_My_President","surface_form":"Kisses for My President","offset":216},{"uri":"Follow_Me%2C_Boys%21","surface_form":"Follow Me, Boys!","offset":253},{"uri":"The_West_Point_Story_(TV_series)","surface_form":"The West Point Story","offset":318},{"uri":"Colt_.45_(TV_series)","surface_form":"Colt.45","offset":342},{"uri":"Sugarfoot","surface_form":"Sugarfoot","offset":353},{"uri":"Cheyenne_(TV_series)","surface_form":"Cheyenne","offset":366},{"uri":"77_Sunset_Strip","surface_form":"77 Sunset Strip","offset":378},{"uri":"Hawaiian_Eye","surface_form":"Hawaiian Eye","offset":397},{"uri":"Surfside_6","surface_form":"Surfside 6","offset":413},{"uri":"The_Roaring_20%27s_(TV_series)","surface_form":"The Roaring 20's","offset":427},{"uri":"Men_into_Space","surface_form":"Men into Space","offset":447},{"uri":"Barnaby_Jones